{"tid":1193053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班垃圾3毛周圍叫人唔好上街，話會有風險喎！","createTime":"2019-06-08T17:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T18:24:17.000Z","uid":31405,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61f8bb82ef4b5399d7bb3e842b01964aae556315","tid":1193053,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:30:18.000Z","msg":"你班垃圾為左幫共產黨為穩，賺個些小錢<br />\n無所不用其極，周圍洗太平地<br />\n<br />\n你同我地講有風險又話有危險無謂斷送自己前途<br />\n<br />\n咁我想同你班垃圾講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果任由逃犯條例通過左，咁香港人個刻已經無晒前途無晒希望，到時既香港人亦已經無野可以再輸<br />\n要賠上既梗加係個人既言論同自由<br />\n<br />\n所以我地一班有良知既香港人聽日就梗加要上街同你班垃圾死過</span></span>"},{"pid":"202f9c2d92bf983764bcd33f5947430d374190f8","tid":1193053,"uid":52230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eead0dbbc9b69e282e57247eec92d1668ee01931","tid":1193053,"uid":119667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"佢地出黎咪有風險囉"},{"pid":"b885ad4b58b01594325cb7935a3fc4dbc6889e1b","tid":1193053,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T17:47:45.000Z","msg":"3毛死未"},{"pid":"99e9782935eab270bd557fa5c44389d1f55ca64d","tid":1193053,"uid":59163,"lik